snippet.textDisplay: I have dreams like that all the time. I've said it for years. The first one that I remember I had, I dreamed we had a spelling test at school. The words I had dreamed were actually on the spelling test the next day. It happens all the time. I dreamt my friend's dad died and the next day she texted me saying that he had passed away, I've dreamt about multiple friends dating certain people and then they do, I've dreamt about people cheating on my friends or my friends cheating on their partners and then they have, people breaking bone and they do, people getting sick and they are.I've had dreams of people doing something in exact spots that end up happening in that exact spot. It's kinda scary and it happens all the time. Not everything I dream is something that happens so I wouldn't say I can predict the future but I get scared cause I don't know if something is going to happen in real life or if its just a dream. It's been happening since I was about 7 and I'm 18 now so I'm kind of used to it now. I've never heard of anyone else that has the same thing
